Fit a line by hand to the
data before 1970.

00:03:10.750 --> 00:03:12.660
So what they want to do, is they
want me to look at all of

00:03:12.660 --> 00:03:14.370
the data before 1970.

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:18.200
So let's see, this is
1970 right here.

00:03:18.200 --> 00:03:20.460
That's 1970 right there.

00:03:20.460 --> 00:03:26.420
They want to fit a line by hand
to the data before 1970.

00:03:26.420 --> 00:03:29.650
What they mean is-- and I'm just
going to eyeball -- but

00:03:29.650 --> 00:03:34.830
