00:04:15.620 --> 00:04:18.130
It would have been nice to
have a line drawing tool.

00:04:18.130 --> 00:04:20.329
Maybe the line might look
something like that.

00:04:20.329 --> 00:04:23.880
There are actual mathematical
ways to figure out the best

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:25.040
fit line on this.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.530
We won't go into
that right now.

00:04:26.530 --> 00:04:28.100
That's called linear
